Package: COMICS
Title: Integrating Selection Scans via C.O.M.I.C.S.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Omar", "Cornejo", email = "omcornej@ucsc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4076-4227"))
Description: A Shiny application for integrated selection scan analysis. COMICS 
    (Combined Outlier Method for Identifying Candidate Signals) provides tools
    for performing ICS (Invariant Coordinate Selection) analysis on genomic data,
    visualizing results, and identifying outliers across multiple selection tests.
